      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu apflep tohß ar Slepfchanu pee tewin preefsch ikkurxa Gresnibas/ tu paglahb tohs Dshwokli preefsch Reektu Mehlehin."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Slawehts lai irr tas KUNGS/ jo wiꞥſch irr favou Schehlastibu brihuigi inan parahdijs/ weenâ stipra Pilsfahtaâ."
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Gann es fazziju eekſch manna Ahtruma: Es efmu ne tawu Azzu Preefschas atineſts/ tatichu tu klaufiſt inannas Sir̄ds Luhgſchanas Balſti / kad es tewis veefauzn."
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Mthlejeet to KUNGU wiſſi winna Swehtee / tas KUNGS paſarga tohs Tizzi-gos/ un maſfa tati papillain/ kas Lepnibu dsenn."
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Effeet drohſchi/ un nem-meetees stiipru Sir̄di/ wiſſi kas us to KUNGU zerre."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Weena kraſfchua Dseefma/eekſch ka mahzihtestoyp / ka ta ihſtena Taiſniba stahtw eekſch Grehku Peedohſchanas : 1 / 2. Rahda breefmiga Leeta tee Grehki eſſu : 3. Ar weenu jauku Zsjuhdſechann to Grehko : 5. Un Pamahziſchana/ ka pehz eedabbucag Grehku Peedohſchanag buhs turretees : 8 / re.\n\nW Eena Pamahzitchana Dahwida.\n\nSwehtigs irr tas/ kam tahs Pahrkahpſchanas irr peedohtas/ kam tee Grehki irr ais-klahti."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Swehtigs irr tas Ziltweks/ kam tas KUNGU tohs Noseegumus ne peelihdsina/ un kurra Garrá Wiltibas newaid."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad es kluffu zeetu/ panthke manni Rauli/ zaar mnu Kauffchanu zaaru Deenu."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tawa Rot ka bija Dnas un Naktis us man gruhtka mans Sattums nokalte/ (tin ka) Waſfaras Bullá/Se"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "(Tadehl) fuhdſu es tmannus Grehkus/ un ne aptla ju mannas Noseegumus/es zijiu/ es tsfazzifchu tam KuSAM mannas Pahrkahpſchnas/ tad peedewi tu mannuGreku Noseegumus/ Sela."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Par to peehuags tewis wti Swehtee ihſtena Atraſchana Laiká/tadeht jepſchu leeli UhdenPuhdi nahktu/ tatſchu tee tonne aishems."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu effi mans Patwruins/ patargi mann no Baifschanas/ tu pulzeſi fahrt manim tahs Bestifchanas Gawifschanu/ Sela."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es dohſchu tew Saprefchanu/ un mahziſchu tew to Zeku/ pa kuuxu ja-eet / es dohſchbPadohmu / manna Azz palterwin buhs."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ne effeet ta/ ka Sirgi uSirg-Ebseti / kam Prahtanwaid/ kam Eemauti un LauschMutte jaleek/ kad tee ne gribp tewin klaht nahkt."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tam Besdeewigam idauds Sahpes/ bet kas ustKUNGU zerre/ topaschu Schelastiba aptkamps."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Preezajeetees eekſch tKUNGA / un lihgſmojectecjut"
    }
